Raytheon Co said the UnitedStates Navy awarded it a 215.3 mln dlr contract to produce1,927 AIM/RIM-7M Sparrow Missile Guidance and Control Sectionsand associated hardware.    Under the contract, the company said it will providemissiles and associated hardware to the U.S. Navy and Air Forceand to several U.S. allies.    Raytheon said the contract represents the major share ofthe fiscal 1987 competitive Sparrow missile procurement. Reuter&#3;